{"tid":1048974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撚完未呀…【中美貿易戰】美國務卿：特朗普不會接受不完美協議！！！支爆定唔支爆？？","createTime":"2019-03-06T03:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T15:27:09.000Z","uid":173631,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ac623de316419448855b034ec7690a8d8e6ddd50","tid":1048974,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:17:21.000Z","msg":"白宮官員近日為貿易戰吹暖風，惟《路透》報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">美國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）最新指特朗普將不會接受不完美協議，並指協議必須有利美國，相信美方會取得想要的結果。蓬佩奧亦稱，美國仍為協議磋商。</span><br />\n被問及特朗普是否會放棄所有不完美的協議，蓬佩奧表示肯定，又指早前「特金會」中，特朗普已拒絕和北韓達成協議。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190306/59335650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190306%2F59335650&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=0ebabde5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190306%2F59335650&h=3ac7ddbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190306/59335650</a>"},{"pid":"7a4682ebceeae7962a61f03951c18a3fa9c64910","tid":1048974,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b411ca39e1176fb5762f122d0011ffe5ba095c","tid":1048974,"uid":41245,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:25:31.000Z","msg":"「trump要政績論」又要出動"},{"pid":"7e8d46ecf9043caf12960a05b8e43d2e2bfa6d9b","tid":1048974,"uid":185085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"班人咁耐都仲未知侵係點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde8a6db8eb8ce3c76667a948899bb14f0bfa042","tid":1048974,"uid":213858,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"有真實人名既消息，肯定比嗰d所謂既據知情人士/白宮內部官員透露既消息要準。"},{"pid